Package com.opengamma.strata.collect.io

Provides utilities for the management of input and output.

In general, the facilities of Guava should be used. In particular, see Files, ByteStreams and CharStreams.

This package adds specific extensions to handle resources and specific file formats.

    A byte source implementation that explicitly wraps a byte array.
    AsciiTable
    An ASCII table generator.
    BeanByteSource
